{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/add-venv-lsp-python/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ec34fd16-c75c-5d0a-9a2d-abdbe04b541b","html":"<p>自从微软的<a href=\"https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Language Server Protocol</a>横空出世后，现代编辑器的使用体验得到了巨大的提升，Emacs这样的老古董也迎来了第二春。</p>\n<p>目前Emacs社区实现了两个lsp client，分别是<code class=\"language-text\">lsp-mode</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">eglot</code>,两个客户端的异同比较见 <a href=\"https://github.com/joaotavora/eglot/issues/180\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">lsp-mode vs eglot</a>，我个人更倾向<code class=\"language-text\">lsp-mode</code>。</p>\n<p>在尝试用<code class=\"language-text\">lsp</code>来写<code class=\"language-text\">python</code>的过程中，我发现它似乎没有很好的支持<code class=\"language-text\">virtualenv</code>，因此在此记录下我的解决方案。</p>\n<!--more-->\n<p>我的方法大体上是参考了<code class=\"language-text\">vscode</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">pycharm</code>，在项目中通过文件的形式记录<code class=\"language-text\">virtualenv</code>的路径，然后加载对应的<code class=\"language-text\">virtualenv</code>，再去启动<code class=\"language-text\">virtualenv</code>中的<code class=\"language-text\">language server</code>。</p>\n<p>考虑以上过程，我们需要</p>\n<ol>\n<li>检测项目跟路径来寻找记录文件</li>\n<li>读取文件内容</li>\n<li>根据内容加载<code class=\"language-text\">virtualenv</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Emacs内置的<code class=\"language-text\">project</code>和社区的<a href=\"https://github.com/bbatsov/projectile\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">projectile</a>都可以方便的检测项目的跟路径, 不过文件处理相关的api，内置的比较粗糙，我采用了<a href=\"https://github.com/rejeep/f.el\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">f</a>这个文件库，另外使用<a href=\"https://github.com/jorgenschaefer/pyvenv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">pyvenv</a>可以方便的加载<code class=\"language-text\">virtualenv</code>。</p>\n<p>更细节一些</p>\n<ol>\n<li>获取项目跟路径<code class=\"language-text\">projectile-project-root</code></li>\n<li>判断文件是否存在<code class=\"language-text\">f-exists?</code>，读取文件<code class=\"language-text\">f-read</code></li>\n<li>加载virtualenv<code class=\"language-text\">pyvenv-workon</code></li>\n</ol>\n<p>最终代码</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"elisp\"><pre class=\"language-elisp\"><code class=\"language-elisp\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">require</span> <span class=\"token quoted-symbol variable symbol\">'f</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">require</span> <span class=\"token quoted-symbol variable symbol\">'subr-x</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">;; 字符串处理api</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">require</span> <span class=\"token quoted-symbol variable symbol\">'projectile</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">nil</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">t</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">use-package</span> pyvenv\n  <span class=\"token lisp-property property\">:ensure</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">t</span>\n  <span class=\"token lisp-property property\">:after</span> python\n  <span class=\"token lisp-property property\">:config</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">;; 使用conda来管理虚拟环境</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">setenv</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"WORKON_HOME\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">expand-file-name</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"~/anaconda3/envs/\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">use-package</span> lsp\n  <span class=\"token lisp-property property\">:ensure</span> lsp-mode\n  <span class=\"token lisp-property property\">:after</span> pyvenv\n  <span class=\"token lisp-property property\">:config</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">add-hook</span> <span class=\"token quoted-symbol variable symbol\">'python-mode-hook</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token lambda\"><span class=\"token keyword\">lambda</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token arguments\"></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span>\n              <span class=\"token comment\">;; 将项目跟路径与存放virtualenv名称的文件.conda-env拼接成完整的路径</span>\n              <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">env_file</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">concat</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">projectile-project-root</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".conda-env\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                <span class=\"token comment\">;; 当文件确实存在则读取，否则提示用户</span>\n                <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">f-exists</span>? env_file<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">venv_name</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">f-read</span> env_file <span class=\"token quoted-symbol variable symbol\">'utf-8</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                      <span class=\"token comment\">;; 去除文件中多余的空格</span>\n                      <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">pyvenv-workon</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">string-trim</span> venv_name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                      <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token car\">lsp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                    <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">message</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"No conda env file found.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>目前，<code class=\"language-text\">lsp-python</code>对<code class=\"language-text\">python</code>的支持已经不错了，不过我不是很喜欢<code class=\"language-text\">lsp-ui</code>的做法，并且<del><code class=\"language-text\">pyls</code>依赖的<code class=\"language-text\">jedi</code>当前版本有无限增加子进程的问题，见 <a href=\"https://emacs-china.org/t/jedi-fork-python/7340\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">jedi fork大量python进程</a></del>（update: <a href=\"https://github.com/davidhalter/jedi/pull/1238\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Fix environment cache regression</a>）。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/add-venv-lsp-python/","tagSlugs":["/tag/emacs/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2018-11-04T22:40:32.169Z","description":"自从微软的 Language Server Protocol 横空出世后，现代编辑器的使用体验得到了巨大的提升，Emacs这样的老古董也迎来了第二春。","tags":["Emacs"],"title":"为lsp python添加virtualenv支持","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/add-venv-lsp-python/"}}}